00:00:17.685 --> 00:00:18.561 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>洛缤！</c>

00:00:18.644 --> 00:00:19.478 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>前情提要</c>

00:00:19.562 --> 00:00:21.021 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我听说洛缤的事了</c>

00:00:21.105 --> 00:00:23.607 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她当时并不是在街道上
她离那个路牙有一步之遥</c>

00:00:23.691 --> 00:00:26.110 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-不好意思 你是谁？
-我叫布彻尔 比利布彻尔</c>

00:00:26.193 --> 00:00:29.238 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>超人类每年间接害死几百人</c>

00:00:29.321 --> 00:00:31.490 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-但这正是我发挥作用之处
-发挥什么作用？</c>

00:00:35.286 --> 00:00:36.996 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>听着 法兰奇 我需要你帮忙 伙计</c>

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:40.249 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-他是谁？
-这位是休伊坎贝尔</c>

00:00:45.671 --> 00:00:47.214 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>休伊 这位是母亲乳汁</c>

00:00:48.424 --> 00:00:50.176 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-她是谁？
-她是超人类恐怖分子</c>

00:00:50.217 --> 00:00:51.177 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她叫喜美子</c>

00:00:54.805 --> 00:00:56.891 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我一直希望能进入超级七人队</c>

00:00:56.974 --> 00:00:59.435 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>请欢迎星光</c>

00:01:00.019 --> 00:01:02.396 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这只关乎你到底有多渴望进入超级七人队</c>

00:01:03.606 --> 00:01:07.443 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们将会把你派驻俄亥俄州桑达斯基一段时间</c>

00:01:09.445 --> 00:01:10.863 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-对了 我叫休伊
-我叫安妮</c>

00:01:10.946 --> 00:01:12.198 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你想要我的号码？</c>

00:01:15.868 --> 00:01:18.287 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>休伊 你的舌头几乎都快</c>

00:01:18.370 --> 00:01:20.206 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>伸进了对手的喉咙里</c>

00:01:20.289 --> 00:01:22.124 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-她不是个坏人
-她是超人类</c>

00:01:22.208 --> 00:01:24.210 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>休坎贝尔杀死了透明人</c>

00:01:24.293 --> 00:01:25.169 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要是他有帮手呢？</c>

00:01:26.128 --> 00:01:28.339 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你的手放下来 放在身体两边</c>

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:30.132 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你必须解释 休伊</c>

00:01:30.216 --> 00:01:32.134 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你曾是唯一我可以信赖的人</c>

00:01:32.218 --> 00:01:33.219 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>五号化合物才是其中的关键</c>

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:35.137 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>它让超人类具有超能力</c>

00:01:35.179 --> 00:01:37.389 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你在说什么？我们天生就有超能力</c>

00:01:39.266 --> 00:01:40.726 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这可真吓人</c>

00:01:42.478 --> 00:01:45.356 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有人会让超人类进入国家防御系统</c>

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:47.399 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们待在后面
否则我就用激光射你们！</c>

00:01:48.484 --> 00:01:52.363 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但如果他们让我们进入军事防御系统
那就不会再次发生这种事</c>

00:01:52.446 --> 00:01:54.198 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我了解失去亲人的感受</c>

00:01:54.281 --> 00:01:56.659 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人强奸了我妻子贝嘉</c>

00:01:56.742 --> 00:01:58.494 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你和我 我们在同一条船上</c>

00:02:07.586 --> 00:02:09.839 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们得回去救他们 这永远不会停止</c>

00:02:09.922 --> 00:02:11.131 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>只会有更多的鲜血</c>

00:02:11.215 --> 00:02:13.592 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果你不喜欢玩 为什么要加入团队？</c>

00:02:17.012 --> 00:02:19.473 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你没有跟布彻尔一起来？
-对</c>

00:02:22.935 --> 00:02:24.353 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没子弹了</c>

00:02:28.357 --> 00:02:30.985 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你来了
-我是个该死的超级英雄</c>

00:02:32.611 --> 00:02:33.863 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想他心脏病发作了</c>

00:02:36.866 --> 00:02:39.994 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再也没有秘密 你答应过我的</c>

00:02:45.583 --> 00:02:46.667 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 伙计</c>

00:02:47.459 --> 00:02:48.627 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我是你父亲</c>

00:02:50.671 --> 00:02:51.547 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>贝嘉</c>

00:03:12.776 --> 00:03:14.653 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>美国国防部</c>

00:03:17.156 --> 00:03:18.490 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>羽衣甘蓝嫩叶沙拉？</c>

00:03:21.243 --> 00:03:22.912 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我现在讲第134页</c>

00:03:23.412 --> 00:03:24.955 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>指挥链不适用于</c>

00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:26.749 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>其他在战场的军事承包商</c>

00:03:26.832 --> 00:03:28.167 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不明白我们为何受此约束</c>

00:03:28.250 --> 00:03:29.543 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>卡普里奶酪三明治？</c>

00:03:29.627 --> 00:03:33.714 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们的超级英雄真正参战时
到底向谁报告？</c>

00:03:34.715 --> 00:03:36.133 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>由始至终都向同一个人报告</c>

00:03:36.634 --> 00:03:37.968 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我</c>

00:03:39.053 --> 00:03:41.347 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>叙利亚扎巴达尼</c>

00:03:54.401 --> 00:03:56.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>辣味鸡肉香菜卷？</c>

00:03:56.362 --> 00:03:57.696 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>小标题16</c>

00:03:57.780 --> 00:04:01.742 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们需要为五号化合物起一个
经过背景核查的最高机密的正式名称</c>

00:04:01.825 --> 00:04:02.785 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>得了吧 史丹</c>

00:04:02.868 --> 00:04:04.411 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>只有一个人有权批准这要求</c>

00:04:04.495 --> 00:04:07.456 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你想走进总统办公室 开始发号施令？</c>

00:04:07.539 --> 00:04:08.999 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那当然了</c>

00:04:09.083 --> 00:04:12.211 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们一半的超级英雄
不知道自己血液里有五号化合物</c>

00:04:12.294 --> 00:04:13.629 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你想让中国知道这事？</c>

00:04:32.898 --> 00:04:34.024 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这个</c>

00:04:34.108 --> 00:04:36.318 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“尽最大努力减少附带性损害”？</c>

00:04:36.402 --> 00:04:38.070 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们希望用词更强烈</c>

00:04:38.153 --> 00:04:41.699 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这是我们纽约合约的标准用语
洛杉矶、芝加哥…</c>

00:04:41.782 --> 00:04:45.202 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们谈的伤亡人数限额到底是多少？</c>

00:04:45.327 --> 00:04:47.746 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>正式的限额？当然是零</c>

00:04:47.830 --> 00:04:50.791 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我们私下的协定？34%</c>

00:04:52.209 --> 00:04:53.544 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>蔬菜意式烘蛋？</c>

00:04:54.878 --> 00:04:57.798 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要不“以我圣火之神力”？</c>

00:04:57.881 --> 00:05:00.634 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这太啰嗦了 口号得朗朗上口</c>

00:05:00.718 --> 00:05:02.469 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要不…</c>

00:05:03.262 --> 00:05:05.347 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“在真相中燃烧”</c>

00:05:05.597 --> 00:05:08.225 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这个口号好</c>

00:05:09.393 --> 00:05:10.269 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得…</c>

00:05:17.901 --> 00:05:19.236 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>在真相中燃烧！</c>

00:06:10.496 --> 00:06:12.372 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>今天我能向美国人民报告</c>

00:06:12.456 --> 00:06:15.459 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>玄色实施了一项行动</c>

00:06:15.542 --> 00:06:18.128 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>杀死了名为“纳奇伯”的超级恐怖分子</c>

00:06:23.342 --> 00:06:25.969 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但那并不意味着不会再有牺牲</c>

00:06:27.679 --> 00:06:30.099 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>令人伤心的是 对这一点的证明…</c>

00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:33.143 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>就在我们眼前</c>

00:06:33.227 --> 00:06:35.354 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人
1980年-2020年</c>

00:06:35.437 --> 00:06:38.565 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>今天 我们为超级七人队
一位早逝的成员哀悼</c>

00:06:39.858 --> 00:06:41.235 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人</c>

00:06:41.318 --> 00:06:43.737 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>被残酷谋杀</c>

00:06:43.821 --> 00:06:46.740 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>主谋是超级恐怖分子联盟“超级恶魔”</c>

00:06:50.119 --> 00:06:51.245 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人在世时</c>

00:06:52.579 --> 00:06:54.832 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他跟我说…</c>

00:06:56.667 --> 00:07:00.462 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他像是早就预料到了他会有不测 他说</c>

00:07:01.130 --> 00:07:02.506 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“嘿 祖国人…</c>

00:07:04.091 --> 00:07:06.051 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“告诉我儿子马维里克我爱他”</c>

00:07:08.595 --> 00:07:09.930 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他还说</c>

00:07:11.181 --> 00:07:13.267 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“你一定要找到那些超级恐怖分子…”</c>

00:07:13.809 --> 00:07:17.855 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>其实该用“超级恶人”这个词 不过他说</c>

00:07:17.938 --> 00:07:22.651 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“你一定要把他们搜出来 祖国人
一定要阻止他们”</c>

00:07:23.152 --> 00:07:25.404 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以我告诉你 马维里克</c>

00:07:26.238 --> 00:07:31.410 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>并告诉这个伟大国家所有的子女们
我一定会阻止他们</c>

00:07:34.163 --> 00:07:35.622 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我会拯救你们</c>

00:07:40.252 --> 00:07:42.129 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我会为你们努力</c>

00:07:44.089 --> 00:07:45.632 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>为美国…</c>

00:07:54.141 --> 00:07:57.728 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>为一位亲爱的老朋友努力</c>

00:08:02.691 --> 00:08:04.109 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再见 兄弟</c>

00:08:07.112 --> 00:08:08.280 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢你</c>

00:08:19.583 --> 00:08:22.836 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们的英雄保卫我们</c>

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:25.422 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你是精英之一</c>

00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:28.717 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>保护我们不受邪恶的伤害</c>

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:30.844 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你超越了其他人</c>

00:08:31.345 --> 00:08:34.514 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>尽管我们能透视你</c>

00:08:34.598 --> 00:08:39.436 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我们承认 我们似乎并不了解你</c>

00:08:40.729 --> 00:08:42.606 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>感谢你所做的一切</c>

00:08:42.689 --> 00:08:44.775 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们大家得到保佑</c>

00:08:45.817 --> 00:08:50.447 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我们的英雄不朽</c>

00:08:51.823 --> 00:08:56.912 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你的精神充满了天空</c>

00:08:58.205 --> 00:09:00.582 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你的存在让我们得到真正的保佑</c>

00:09:00.666 --> 00:09:02.876 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>从一开始就如此</c>

00:09:04.253 --> 00:09:08.423 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你将永远不会从我们心中消逝</c>

00:09:09.258 --> 00:09:11.385 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-搞错 那是我的肩膀
-什么？</c>

00:09:11.468 --> 00:09:12.928 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>就在那里</c>

00:09:13.512 --> 00:09:15.222 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那他妈的是我的肩膀 他们…</c>

00:09:16.932 --> 00:09:18.433 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们把我从照片里截掉了</c>

00:09:18.517 --> 00:09:20.602 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们不能把我从照片里删掉</c>

00:09:20.686 --> 00:09:21.979 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们不能把我删掉</c>

00:09:22.062 --> 00:09:24.314 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 够了 该走了</c>

00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:27.859 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再给我一杯岩浆喷发 麻烦了</c>

00:09:27.943 --> 00:09:30.696 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我说了 该走了 否则我就打给爆料网站</c>

00:09:41.331 --> 00:09:43.667 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>眼不见 一直挂念</c>

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.752 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>两件64美元</c>

00:09:46.420 --> 00:09:48.630 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>眼不见 一直挂念</c>

00:09:48.714 --> 00:09:50.340 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>两件64美元</c>

00:09:51.091 --> 00:09:52.926 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>眼不见 一直挂念</c>

00:09:56.471 --> 00:09:57.806 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们看见你了
1980年-2020年</c>

00:10:07.691 --> 00:10:10.277 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很高兴见到你们 谢谢</c>

00:10:10.694 --> 00:10:12.362 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的 别难过</c>

00:10:13.697 --> 00:10:15.615 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我知道 我也想他 伙计</c>

00:10:16.533 --> 00:10:18.785 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢大家 这意义非凡</c>

00:10:22.998 --> 00:10:24.541 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人 星光</c>

00:10:24.624 --> 00:10:25.876 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-嗨 大卫
-大卫</c>

00:10:25.959 --> 00:10:27.878 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>超级七人塔里各位的心情如何？</c>

00:10:27.961 --> 00:10:30.589 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>说实话</c>

00:10:30.672 --> 00:10:32.883 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很难过 实在很难过</c>

00:10:33.008 --> 00:10:34.718 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人葬礼
祖国人与星光出席</c>

00:10:34.801 --> 00:10:36.720 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>事发太突然了 你知道吗？</c>

00:10:36.803 --> 00:10:38.305 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的 但这位英雄</c>

00:10:38.388 --> 00:10:40.515 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他一直是我们的顶梁柱</c>

00:10:40.932 --> 00:10:43.101 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他让我们坐下来 告诉我们说</c>

00:10:43.185 --> 00:10:45.270 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“我们不只是一支团队 我们是一家人</c>

00:10:45.354 --> 00:10:47.105 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“我们必须像一家人一样团结起来”</c>

00:10:48.982 --> 00:10:51.568 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>星光 谢谢你这番话</c>

00:10:51.651 --> 00:10:53.028 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢你才是</c>

00:10:53.111 --> 00:10:55.614 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>真的 没有你的话 我真不知道我们会如何</c>

00:10:56.990 --> 00:10:58.158 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她真是最棒的</c>

00:10:59.034 --> 00:11:00.410 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她真是最棒的</c>

00:11:00.494 --> 00:11:01.745 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们俩…</c>

00:11:30.399 --> 00:11:36.363 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>英雄克星</c>

00:12:27.497 --> 00:12:29.749 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>克拉克森大道
永远的海地王</c>

00:12:49.686 --> 00:12:50.896 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很好</c>

00:13:13.835 --> 00:13:14.961 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你去什么地方？</c>

00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:19.216 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>只是想去给你买洗手液</c>

00:13:22.844 --> 00:13:25.055 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>买芦荟那种 然后马上回来</c>

00:13:25.138 --> 00:13:27.182 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>行 知道了 芦荟 非常好</c>

00:13:27.265 --> 00:13:29.226 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让你的皮肤保持光滑 好的</c>

00:13:41.613 --> 00:13:42.447 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>经典超级英雄漫画 此处有售！</c>

00:14:01.341 --> 00:14:04.928 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>《公民星光 》 今年秋天 沃特隆重推出</c>

00:14:05.637 --> 00:14:07.389 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>正义从未如此赏心悦目</c>

00:14:15.689 --> 00:14:18.024 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嫌疑凶手逍遥法外
屠夫比利？</c>

00:14:33.456 --> 00:14:35.875 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那部一次性手机 你把芯卡折断了吗？</c>

00:14:35.959 --> 00:14:36.960 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>老天</c>

00:14:38.003 --> 00:14:40.422 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你上次睡觉是什么时候？
-低下头</c>

00:14:41.006 --> 00:14:42.173 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对不起 我只是…</c>

00:14:44.175 --> 00:14:46.803 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我被人通缉而你正当红 所以…</c>

00:14:48.847 --> 00:14:51.349 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你到底有没有折断芯卡 还是…
-有</c>

00:14:51.433 --> 00:14:53.018 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我把芯卡折断了 行了吧？</c>

00:14:53.101 --> 00:14:55.270 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有人跟踪我来这里</c>

00:14:55.353 --> 00:14:57.564 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我在这下面 他们根本追踪不了我</c>

00:14:57.981 --> 00:14:59.149 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们很安全</c>

00:15:05.572 --> 00:15:07.032 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你很好看</c>

00:15:07.907 --> 00:15:09.826 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是 你也很帅气</c>

00:15:09.909 --> 00:15:12.078 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你看起来 就是…</c>

00:15:14.497 --> 00:15:16.833 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 我在胡扯 对不起</c>

00:15:16.916 --> 00:15:18.543 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你很憔悴
-我知道</c>

00:15:19.336 --> 00:15:20.462 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我知道</c>

00:15:21.087 --> 00:15:22.714 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们住在哪里？</c>

00:15:25.258 --> 00:15:28.011 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>在伊维萨岛的地中海俱乐部 棒极了</c>

00:15:28.678 --> 00:15:31.389 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-泡沫派对能改变你的人生
-白痴</c>

00:15:44.402 --> 00:15:45.487 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>给你</c>

00:15:51.034 --> 00:15:52.410 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>见鬼了</c>

00:15:55.163 --> 00:15:56.456 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我认识他</c>

00:15:57.374 --> 00:15:59.376 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-真的？
-是的 我是说</c>

00:15:59.459 --> 00:16:03.463 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>已经好久没联系了 不过是的
在我参加“基督的披风”时认识的</c>

00:16:05.173 --> 00:16:07.592 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你确定你下得了手？</c>

00:16:08.343 --> 00:16:09.719 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我有选择吗？</c>

00:16:18.311 --> 00:16:22.023 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 我看到你在青少年选择奖上</c>

00:16:22.107 --> 00:16:24.818 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一张很棒的合影 跟那家伙 他叫什么来着？</c>

00:16:24.901 --> 00:16:26.736 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>安塞尔亚当斯？</c>

00:16:27.529 --> 00:16:29.447 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>安尔顿埃尔格特</c>

00:16:31.241 --> 00:16:33.493 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你是在照片墙上跟踪我吗？
-没有</c>

00:16:33.576 --> 00:16:36.037 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有 当然没有 你少自恋了</c>

00:16:36.121 --> 00:16:38.123 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是公关部的人把你俩凑在一起的 还是…</c>

00:16:38.206 --> 00:16:39.582 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是 他这人不错</c>

00:16:39.666 --> 00:16:40.667 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他是个演员</c>

00:16:40.750 --> 00:16:45.046 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他是一个没有每天当着我的面撒谎的演员</c>

00:16:47.507 --> 00:16:49.801 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 行 我明白了 伤心啊</c>

00:16:53.263 --> 00:16:55.223 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对不起 我…</c>

00:16:55.515 --> 00:16:56.683 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>休伊 我只是…</c>

00:17:03.189 --> 00:17:04.399 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿</c>

00:17:05.900 --> 00:17:07.402 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好好睡一觉吧</c>

00:17:09.779 --> 00:17:11.531 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我知道你安全了才睡</c>

00:17:17.287 --> 00:17:19.164 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>飞溅区 桑达斯基</c>

00:17:23.084 --> 00:17:24.461 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们觉得这很好玩？</c>

00:17:25.712 --> 00:17:27.672 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们觉得水是好玩的？</c>

00:17:27.756 --> 00:17:31.342 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>在马里亚纳海沟游泳试试看
你们这些该死的小笨蛋</c>

00:17:32.093 --> 00:17:34.012 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对的 那里不太好玩</c>

00:17:34.846 --> 00:17:37.640 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不好玩 那里又暗又冷</c>

00:17:37.724 --> 00:17:39.893 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而且只有自己一个人</c>

00:17:41.936 --> 00:17:45.023 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他妈的无比孤独</c>

00:17:55.366 --> 00:17:56.785 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你自由了 小鱼儿</c>

00:17:56.868 --> 00:17:58.161 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你被保释了</c>

00:18:09.756 --> 00:18:10.757 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 兄弟</c>

00:18:12.050 --> 00:18:12.967 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>喝瓶橘子汽水？</c>

00:18:15.512 --> 00:18:16.721 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢</c>

00:18:16.805 --> 00:18:18.223 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 我认识你</c>

00:18:18.306 --> 00:18:20.183 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 你叫渡鸦…</c>

00:18:20.266 --> 00:18:21.476 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>渡鸦翼</c>

00:18:22.393 --> 00:18:23.853 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是老鹰</c>

00:18:23.937 --> 00:18:25.980 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>克里夫兰的神箭手老鹰？</c>

00:18:26.064 --> 00:18:28.858 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们在沃特展上见过大概五次 我是说…</c>

00:18:28.942 --> 00:18:30.902 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 那不重要</c>

00:18:31.653 --> 00:18:33.446 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-是你把我保释出来的？
-对</c>

00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:35.198 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>为什么？</c>

00:18:35.281 --> 00:18:37.784 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>因为即使是英雄 偶尔也需要援手</c>

00:18:37.867 --> 00:18:39.118 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>来吧</c>

00:18:42.288 --> 00:18:45.416 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人特许经销电影系列 尤其是《隐形力量2》…</c>

00:18:45.500 --> 00:18:46.876 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>塞斯罗根回忆透明人</c>

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:48.962 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>《深度透视 克里斯汉森主持》
案情重演</c>

00:18:49.045 --> 00:18:51.881 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>求你了！我的孩子需要妈妈！</c>

00:18:51.965 --> 00:18:53.049 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>噢！</c>

00:18:53.466 --> 00:18:55.969 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>闭上你的贱嘴 你这蠢货</c>

00:18:56.052 --> 00:18:58.596 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>否则我就炸死你</c>

00:18:59.722 --> 00:19:02.851 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但那正是威廉布彻尔所做的事</c>

00:19:02.934 --> 00:19:06.312 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他谋杀了沃特副总裁玛德琳斯蒂尔威尔</c>

00:19:06.396 --> 00:19:09.858 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>用了超过13公斤C4炸药</c>

00:19:09.941 --> 00:19:11.568 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>威廉布彻尔为什么那么做？</c>

00:19:11.651 --> 00:19:14.863 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>也许是为了他的亡妻 一名前沃特雇员</c>

00:19:14.946 --> 00:19:16.447 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而心怀怨恨</c>

00:19:16.990 --> 00:19:19.409 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>玛德琳斯蒂尔威尔的孩子为什么</c>

00:19:19.492 --> 00:19:23.705 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>会在27公里外的一个院子里平安无事？</c>

00:19:23.788 --> 00:19:24.914 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这是个谜</c>

00:19:25.790 --> 00:19:27.333 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>屠夫先生在哪里？</c>

00:19:28.710 --> 00:19:31.129 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-他为什么没打电话来？
-谁在乎啊？</c>

00:19:32.005 --> 00:19:33.756 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-他可能死了
-不可能</c>

00:19:33.840 --> 00:19:35.675 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他这王八蛋命硬得很</c>

00:19:35.758 --> 00:19:38.219 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>…或他确知的同伙中的任何一个</c>

00:19:38.303 --> 00:19:40.388 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>马文乳汁、休坎贝尔</c>

00:19:40.471 --> 00:19:43.516 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>或这个男人 他的真实身份不明</c>

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:47.395 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>请拨打18880 转“罪案部”</c>

00:19:48.438 --> 00:19:49.564 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>天啊</c>

00:19:52.233 --> 00:19:54.527 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们得马上离开这里</c>

00:19:55.445 --> 00:19:57.488 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好用的护照可不便宜 好吧？</c>

00:19:57.572 --> 00:19:59.657 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我卖火箭推进榴弹 走私AK-47</c>

00:19:59.741 --> 00:20:01.951 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们赚够钱了就走人</c>

00:20:05.330 --> 00:20:06.706 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你会去哪里 小休伊？</c>

00:20:06.789 --> 00:20:09.584 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你可以待在这里 跟法兰奇的黑帮朋友们一起</c>

00:20:09.667 --> 00:20:12.587 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那些小床上有各种精子的味道 你肯定会喜欢的</c>

00:20:13.796 --> 00:20:15.757 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你有更好的主意吗？</c>

00:20:15.840 --> 00:20:18.843 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>或许我们所有人可以待在你妈妈的屁眼里</c>

00:20:18.927 --> 00:20:22.430 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>或者 也许我们不能逃跑</c>

00:20:23.097 --> 00:20:24.974 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你别像复读机一样老重复这话</c>

00:20:25.058 --> 00:20:27.602 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们不能轻易放弃</c>

00:20:27.685 --> 00:20:29.228 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>伙计们 我们搞点五号化合物</c>

00:20:29.312 --> 00:20:31.022 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>拿去给《纽约时报》</c>

00:20:31.105 --> 00:20:32.565 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>把沃特往死里弄</c>

00:20:32.649 --> 00:20:33.775 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你有五号化合物吗 休伊？</c>

00:20:34.150 --> 00:20:35.485 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我可没有</c>

00:20:35.568 --> 00:20:39.614 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们可以搞到一点 有人能帮我们弄到</c>

00:20:39.697 --> 00:20:41.115 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那个人会是谁？</c>

00:20:43.451 --> 00:20:46.120 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你没听电视里怎么说的吗？我们现在出名了</c>

00:20:46.913 --> 00:20:48.748 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-布彻尔更是如此
-去他的布彻尔</c>

00:20:48.831 --> 00:20:51.000 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我们不需要他
-《天龙特攻队》有汉尼拔</c>

00:20:51.084 --> 00:20:53.169 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>《十二金刚》有李马文</c>

00:20:53.252 --> 00:20:54.921 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>披头士有布莱恩爱普斯坦</c>

00:20:55.004 --> 00:20:56.381 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们不需要布彻尔</c>

00:20:56.464 --> 00:20:58.800 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 谁当我们的队长？</c>

00:20:59.634 --> 00:21:00.760 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你？</c>

00:21:01.970 --> 00:21:04.347 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>各位 先听我说…</c>

00:21:04.430 --> 00:21:06.808 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他妈的闭嘴</c>

00:21:11.437 --> 00:21:12.689 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谈话结束</c>

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:01.923 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人 你好</c>

00:23:02.840 --> 00:23:03.925 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>艾诗丽</c>

00:23:05.593 --> 00:23:08.805 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很高兴看到你在这里安顿好了</c>

00:23:08.888 --> 00:23:10.139 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对</c>

00:23:11.641 --> 00:23:13.559 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这里太需要翻修了</c>

00:23:13.643 --> 00:23:17.230 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>感觉这是从2003年穿越来的 你懂吗？</c>

00:23:18.898 --> 00:23:21.734 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我以前喜欢这里
-对 我也是 这里曾经非常棒</c>

00:23:22.568 --> 00:23:26.405 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人 我想再次感谢你推荐我做这份工作</c>

00:23:27.031 --> 00:23:30.618 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我接到电话时太惊讶了</c>

00:23:32.245 --> 00:23:36.165 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我会尽我最大的能力
担起斯蒂尔威尔小姐的职位</c>

00:23:38.251 --> 00:23:39.627 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>愿上帝让她安息</c>

00:23:40.878 --> 00:23:43.506 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的 愿她安息</c>

00:23:43.589 --> 00:23:44.966 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对</c>

00:23:46.759 --> 00:23:49.887 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有没有抓住杀死她的凶手
那个疯子布彻尔？</c>

00:23:51.764 --> 00:23:52.849 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有</c>

00:23:53.724 --> 00:23:54.851 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>还没有</c>

00:23:55.601 --> 00:23:56.644 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我们一定会的</c>

00:23:58.396 --> 00:23:59.897 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有好消息</c>

00:23:59.981 --> 00:24:01.566 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得我找到了一个英雄</c>

00:24:01.649 --> 00:24:03.943 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个顶替透明人的完美人选</c>

00:24:05.611 --> 00:24:06.821 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>真的？</c>

00:24:07.864 --> 00:24:08.823 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这么快？</c>

00:24:08.906 --> 00:24:10.533 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他现在就在健身房</c>

00:24:10.616 --> 00:24:12.493 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你想见他吗？
-我想吗？</c>

00:24:13.619 --> 00:24:14.954 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>带路吧</c>

00:24:26.549 --> 00:24:28.050 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他是盲点 对吧？</c>

00:24:28.134 --> 00:24:30.720 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>超级七人队里一名能力相异的成员</c>

00:24:33.472 --> 00:24:35.391 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>千禧世代肯定会大力支持我们</c>

00:24:35.474 --> 00:24:37.894 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>包容是他们现在最关心的事</c>

00:24:37.977 --> 00:24:38.895 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让人惊叹</c>

00:24:38.978 --> 00:24:41.731 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>然后我认为如果能找到一个少数族裔
或一位女性 如果运气很好的话</c>

00:24:41.814 --> 00:24:44.901 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个少数族裔女性来替代深海
那我们就无敌了</c>

00:24:51.908 --> 00:24:53.576 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人 你…</c>

00:24:54.368 --> 00:24:55.828 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>非常荣幸 先生</c>

00:24:55.912 --> 00:24:57.496 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>慢着</c>

00:24:57.580 --> 00:24:58.456 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>等一下</c>

00:24:58.539 --> 00:24:59.790 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你居然知道是我？</c>

00:25:02.835 --> 00:25:04.754 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>太厉害了</c>

00:25:04.837 --> 00:25:07.506 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有超级耳朵就不需要超级眼睛</c>

00:25:07.590 --> 00:25:10.426 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我必须说 这太神奇了</c>

00:25:10.509 --> 00:25:13.888 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而你 我的朋友 你是真正的英雄</c>

00:25:13.971 --> 00:25:17.099 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是因为你的工作 而是…</c>

00:25:17.934 --> 00:25:20.436 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-而是因为你所克服的困难
-谢谢你</c>

00:25:21.354 --> 00:25:23.272 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你的赞赏对我的意义太重大了</c>

00:25:23.356 --> 00:25:25.858 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>行了 别谦虚了</c>

00:25:25.942 --> 00:25:29.612 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对了 两位 我只有一个问题
不知道能不能问</c>

00:25:29.695 --> 00:25:30.821 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可以</c>

00:25:30.905 --> 00:25:32.490 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-真的？
-真的</c>

00:25:32.573 --> 00:25:34.367 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的 那…</c>

00:25:36.327 --> 00:25:40.206 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果我 怎么说呢 这样做 会如何？</c>

00:25:47.171 --> 00:25:50.758 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在你不过是一个普通、无能、该死的瞎子</c>

00:25:53.552 --> 00:25:55.638 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这肯定是开玩笑</c>

00:25:55.721 --> 00:25:57.306 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>艾诗丽</c>

00:25:58.099 --> 00:26:01.644 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你凭什么认为我会允许
一个残废加入超级七人队？</c>

00:26:01.727 --> 00:26:04.730 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>该死的 艾诗丽 别看他 看着我</c>

00:26:06.315 --> 00:26:07.608 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>艾诗丽！</c>

00:26:08.109 --> 00:26:09.485 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>看着我</c>

00:26:10.403 --> 00:26:12.613 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-对不起
-我们把话说清楚</c>

00:26:13.155 --> 00:26:16.075 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你之所以会在这里 而不是在月经杯公司</c>

00:26:16.158 --> 00:26:17.910 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>做公司公关</c>

00:26:17.994 --> 00:26:19.704 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是因为我把你带到了这里</c>

00:26:19.787 --> 00:26:22.873 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你是可有可无的 这意味着你听从我的命令</c>

00:26:22.957 --> 00:26:24.292 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的</c>

00:26:26.252 --> 00:26:29.547 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>从现在开始 我的议事议程由我来定</c>

00:26:29.630 --> 00:26:32.842 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的营销策略由我来审批
我的讲话要点由我来写</c>

00:26:32.925 --> 00:26:36.929 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你要将99楼发生的一切都告诉我</c>

00:26:37.013 --> 00:26:38.973 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我说的是“一切”</c>

00:26:39.056 --> 00:26:42.893 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>每通电话、每封电邮、每个群聊
就连灯泡烧了</c>

00:26:42.977 --> 00:26:44.478 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你也得向我报告</c>

00:26:44.562 --> 00:26:46.105 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>另外 艾诗丽</c>

00:26:47.440 --> 00:26:49.400 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你完全没有权力</c>

00:26:49.483 --> 00:26:52.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>决定谁能加入超级七人队</c>

00:26:53.738 --> 00:26:54.947 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>由我来决定</c>

00:26:56.782 --> 00:26:58.784 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们是否达成了共识？</c>

00:26:59.493 --> 00:27:00.703 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的</c>

00:27:05.583 --> 00:27:08.085 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>透明人今天下葬 环绕在他身边的是…</c>

00:27:08.169 --> 00:27:09.337 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>妈：请回我的电话 求你了</c>

00:27:09.420 --> 00:27:12.006 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他的家人、朋友、支持者及沃特集团的同事</c>

00:27:12.089 --> 00:27:15.051 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>大家可以观看
星光在追悼会上唱《从未真正消亡》</c>

00:27:15.134 --> 00:27:18.471 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在沃特音乐频道上可看</c>

00:27:18.554 --> 00:27:19.513 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我爱你 果冻豆</c>

00:27:19.597 --> 00:27:21.766 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我会一直向你道歉 回我吧</c>

00:27:26.228 --> 00:27:28.105 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你肯定无法抵抗这场逮捕</c>

00:27:28.189 --> 00:27:29.940 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>美国最性感的打击犯罪者</c>

00:27:30.024 --> 00:27:32.485 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>正用超能力对执法工作进行改头换面</c>

00:27:32.568 --> 00:27:34.028 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>精彩尽在《公民星光》</c>

00:27:34.111 --> 00:27:35.696 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>今年秋天 沃特隆重推出</c>

00:27:35.780 --> 00:27:38.115 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>放马过来 让她…</c>

00:28:18.781 --> 00:28:20.491 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你知道情况的</c>

00:28:20.574 --> 00:28:22.701 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不想被高额清洁账单缠住了</c>

00:28:28.707 --> 00:28:29.959 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好了</c>

00:28:31.544 --> 00:28:33.421 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你有什么要求？</c>

00:28:33.504 --> 00:28:35.131 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你想割一条腿？</c>

00:28:36.632 --> 00:28:38.884 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>其实是一条胳膊 麻烦了</c>

00:28:40.136 --> 00:28:41.387 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>400</c>

00:29:04.118 --> 00:29:08.497 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你想我用锯的、砍的 还是…
-随便你想怎么样 猛男</c>

00:29:25.806 --> 00:29:27.016 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的妈呀</c>

00:29:33.314 --> 00:29:35.065 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不可思议！</c>

00:29:35.149 --> 00:29:36.942 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>天啊 谢谢你！</c>

00:29:37.026 --> 00:29:38.194 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这真的…</c>

00:29:38.861 --> 00:29:40.446 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我能保留这条手臂 对吗？</c>

00:29:41.447 --> 00:29:43.407 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 不过得放冰箱</c>

00:29:48.913 --> 00:29:51.499 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再加一千 我让你砍掉我的小鸡鸡</c>

00:29:56.754 --> 00:29:58.214 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>最近的取款机在哪里？</c>

00:30:21.445 --> 00:30:23.030 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>到底发生了什么事？</c>

00:30:23.113 --> 00:30:24.281 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>见鬼了</c>

00:30:24.365 --> 00:30:26.242 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让他坐下来！把他扶过来这里</c>

00:30:37.670 --> 00:30:38.963 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可怕</c>

00:30:39.046 --> 00:30:40.339 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>听着</c>

00:30:40.422 --> 00:30:42.841 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他手臂的每根骨头都断了
一半的肋骨都断了</c>

00:30:42.925 --> 00:30:44.843 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我无能为力 送他去医院吧</c>

00:30:45.761 --> 00:30:48.847 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>医院 法兰奇 帮我翻译一下
让他送朋友去医院</c>

00:30:52.726 --> 00:30:53.769 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>操！</c>

00:30:57.731 --> 00:30:59.191 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让开</c>

00:31:26.594 --> 00:31:27.886 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他说什么了？发生了什么事？</c>

00:31:31.557 --> 00:31:33.100 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>法兰奇 他说什么了？</c>

00:32:43.545 --> 00:32:45.673 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-警察看到了吗？
-没有人看到</c>

00:32:45.756 --> 00:32:47.883 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我可不想被终身监禁不得保释</c>

00:32:53.055 --> 00:32:55.933 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们向我保证过 只是走私枪支</c>

00:32:56.725 --> 00:32:58.727 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可卡因和芬太尼 而不是该死的…</c>

00:32:58.811 --> 00:33:01.105 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是走私人口？老天爷 法兰奇</c>

00:33:01.188 --> 00:33:03.816 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-他们没有告诉我
-你也没有问</c>

00:33:25.754 --> 00:33:26.922 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个超人类</c>

00:33:28.132 --> 00:33:29.675 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个超人类恐怖分子</c>

00:33:33.595 --> 00:33:36.181 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有人付钱给他们
把一个超人类恐怖分子偷运了进来</c>

00:33:42.604 --> 00:33:43.772 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>最可怕的词？
超级恐怖分子</c>

00:33:43.856 --> 00:33:46.817 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这个如何？这个给你们什么感觉？
有人想说说吗？</c>

00:33:46.900 --> 00:33:49.653 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我讨厌这个词
-这个反应很强烈 玛格丽特</c>

00:33:49.737 --> 00:33:51.405 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想听你解释一下</c>

00:33:51.488 --> 00:33:54.032 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你说讨厌“超级恐怖分子”这个词
是什么意思？</c>

00:33:54.116 --> 00:33:56.160 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的意思就是这个词很让人害怕</c>

00:33:56.243 --> 00:33:58.954 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让我想锁门并躲在床底下</c>

00:33:59.037 --> 00:34:00.664 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这意味着《泰克骑士》</c>

00:34:00.748 --> 00:34:02.624 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>电影首映周末入座率会下降两位数</c>

00:34:02.708 --> 00:34:05.294 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我一直说 “超级恶人”这个词更好</c>

00:34:09.631 --> 00:34:12.217 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>吉尔 问他们觉得“超级恶人”如何</c>

00:34:12.301 --> 00:34:14.261 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那“超级恶人”这个词呢？</c>

00:34:14.887 --> 00:34:18.515 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得听起来好一点
感觉更刺激 更有异国风情</c>

00:34:23.061 --> 00:34:26.523 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的 我们回过头来讨论这些词</c>

00:34:26.607 --> 00:34:28.984 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们更喜欢“拯救美国”吗？</c>

00:34:29.067 --> 00:34:30.611 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>举手表态好吗？</c>

00:34:31.278 --> 00:34:34.239 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的 那“拯救世界”呢？</c>

00:34:34.323 --> 00:34:36.158 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一致同意 反应强烈</c>

00:34:36.241 --> 00:34:37.409 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那 这个词有什么…</c>

00:34:37.493 --> 00:34:39.787 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不行 必须用“拯救美国”</c>

00:34:42.873 --> 00:34:44.041 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不确定</c>

00:34:44.124 --> 00:34:46.293 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得“拯救世界”有…</c>

00:34:51.632 --> 00:34:54.426 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让我们留在军队的是美国人</c>

00:34:54.510 --> 00:34:55.844 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是全世界</c>

00:34:57.012 --> 00:34:58.555 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>必须用“拯救美国”</c>

00:35:01.266 --> 00:35:03.393 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你照办吧</c>

00:35:03.477 --> 00:35:05.020 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很好</c>

00:35:20.285 --> 00:35:21.370 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嘿 伙计</c>

00:35:24.331 --> 00:35:26.166 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢你收留我</c>

00:35:26.250 --> 00:35:29.920 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>抱歉把厕所弄脏了 我会清理干净</c>

00:35:30.546 --> 00:35:32.214 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不需要道歉</c>

00:35:36.385 --> 00:35:37.678 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的</c>

00:35:39.388 --> 00:35:40.973 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>天啊 你吓着我了</c>

00:35:41.181 --> 00:35:43.851 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她是卡萝尔 我的好朋友</c>

00:35:43.934 --> 00:35:47.563 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>卡萝尔 这位是深海</c>

00:35:47.646 --> 00:35:50.274 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我一直期待与你见面 深海</c>

00:35:50.357 --> 00:35:51.775 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要来一瓶橘子汽水吗？</c>

00:35:54.361 --> 00:35:55.571 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢</c>

00:35:58.448 --> 00:36:01.034 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不管如何 不需要道歉</c>

00:36:01.118 --> 00:36:03.704 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们都经历过 确实不好受</c>

00:36:06.623 --> 00:36:08.292 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-经历过什么？
-人生低谷</c>

00:36:10.669 --> 00:36:12.754 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我并不认为我处于人生低谷</c>

00:36:12.838 --> 00:36:16.383 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对我来说 我恍然大悟的时刻</c>

00:36:16.466 --> 00:36:20.137 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是有人质在克罗格被挟持的时候</c>

00:36:20.220 --> 00:36:23.265 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有好几个枪手 我出现了</c>

00:36:23.348 --> 00:36:26.643 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不停地射箭 射得很好</c>

00:36:28.437 --> 00:36:29.646 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但是…</c>

00:36:32.357 --> 00:36:35.527 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个箭筒能装的箭数量有限</c>

00:36:37.404 --> 00:36:39.031 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的箭射完了</c>

00:36:40.324 --> 00:36:41.617 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>然后…</c>

00:36:43.327 --> 00:36:45.245 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们在那天失去了许多好人</c>

00:36:47.164 --> 00:36:49.625 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>然后我就开始质疑了</c>

00:36:50.542 --> 00:36:52.628 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>拿箭来跟半自动手枪比较</c>

00:36:53.712 --> 00:36:56.465 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我明白到了</c>

00:36:57.132 --> 00:37:01.053 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>箭术并非不重要 它是永恒的</c>

00:37:01.136 --> 00:37:04.389 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这是一种纯粹而古老的艺术</c>

00:37:05.974 --> 00:37:07.643 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>卡萝尔帮助我认识到了这一点</c>

00:37:08.518 --> 00:37:10.562 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你是什么人？他的心理治疗师之类的？</c>

00:37:10.646 --> 00:37:11.855 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是</c>

00:37:12.481 --> 00:37:16.109 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 其实心理治疗是很有破坏性的</c>

00:37:16.193 --> 00:37:18.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你可以说我是他的导师</c>

00:37:18.362 --> 00:37:19.780 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那你的情况呢 深海？</c>

00:37:21.406 --> 00:37:23.700 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的…什么情况？</c>

00:37:23.784 --> 00:37:25.202 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你怎么会来到这里的？</c>

00:37:27.329 --> 00:37:28.538 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你可以告诉她 深海</c>

00:37:31.124 --> 00:37:32.376 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>告诉她什么？</c>

00:37:33.585 --> 00:37:36.421 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>关于你酗酒的问题 你的自尊心问题</c>

00:37:36.922 --> 00:37:38.382 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>真正地敞开心扉 深海</c>

00:37:38.465 --> 00:37:40.717 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 我没有酗酒…</c>

00:37:40.801 --> 00:37:42.678 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我没事
-这里很安全 深海</c>

00:37:42.761 --> 00:37:45.555 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果你的自尊心不低</c>

00:37:45.639 --> 00:37:47.891 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那你为什么总是贬低女人？</c>

00:37:47.975 --> 00:37:49.267 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这是个好问题 深海</c>

00:37:49.351 --> 00:37:50.978 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 谢谢你 你猜怎么着</c>

00:37:51.061 --> 00:37:53.188 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我搞不懂这到底是怎么回事
但这太奇怪了</c>

00:37:53.271 --> 00:37:54.189 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以我要走了</c>

00:37:54.731 --> 00:37:56.274 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们只是想帮你</c>

00:37:56.358 --> 00:37:58.193 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>卡萝尔给了我很大的帮助 深海</c>

00:37:58.276 --> 00:38:00.821 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-不用 谢了
-帮助你回到超级七人队</c>

00:38:09.621 --> 00:38:10.664 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>集众教会</c>

00:38:10.747 --> 00:38:12.541 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>目的地
自我更新的科学</c>

00:38:19.172 --> 00:38:22.634 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>昨天 在俄亥俄州桑达斯基的飞溅区
有人发现深海喝醉了</c>

00:38:22.718 --> 00:38:25.512 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>并对孩子们胡言乱语</c>

00:38:25.595 --> 00:38:29.599 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他后来被逮捕
被送去了桑达斯基普通拘留中心</c>

00:38:29.683 --> 00:38:32.477 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>随后他就被保释外出</c>

00:38:33.854 --> 00:38:35.355 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你做的？</c>

00:38:46.575 --> 00:38:47.909 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你写了什么吗？</c>

00:38:50.454 --> 00:38:51.621 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>男孩</c>

00:38:52.873 --> 00:38:54.124 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>什么男孩？</c>

00:38:54.207 --> 00:38:55.834 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不明白</c>

00:38:55.917 --> 00:38:57.169 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>什么男孩？</c>

00:39:06.136 --> 00:39:07.471 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好了 怎么样？</c>

00:39:09.014 --> 00:39:12.309 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>支付他们把那王八蛋偷运进来的钱
是从一个盲账上转过去的</c>

00:39:13.435 --> 00:39:14.603 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有任何线索</c>

00:39:14.686 --> 00:39:16.271 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你那些该死的朋友啊</c>

00:39:16.354 --> 00:39:18.482 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我从来没说过他们是我的朋友</c>

00:39:18.565 --> 00:39:21.068 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我只说了我们在这里会安全</c>

00:39:22.736 --> 00:39:24.613 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 行了 我们怎么办？</c>

00:39:25.322 --> 00:39:27.199 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要不你直接打电话报警吧？</c>

00:39:27.282 --> 00:39:29.117 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>什么？给匿名线报？</c>

00:39:29.201 --> 00:39:31.369 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 好啊 那就会直接上报市长</c>

00:39:31.453 --> 00:39:32.329 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你也看到了录像</c>

00:39:32.412 --> 00:39:35.499 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要是他举起飞机
或者破坏布鲁克林大桥 怎么办？</c>

00:39:35.582 --> 00:39:37.459 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那你有什么大计划 休伊？</c>

00:39:39.377 --> 00:39:41.379 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 不是有那个中情局女探员吗？</c>

00:39:41.463 --> 00:39:42.672 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>瑞尼？</c>

00:39:42.756 --> 00:39:44.174 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对</c>

00:39:44.257 --> 00:39:47.761 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>就是想把我们的蛋蛋当成核桃压碎</c>

00:39:48.553 --> 00:39:50.764 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-那个中情局？
-我们可以打给布彻尔</c>

00:39:50.847 --> 00:39:53.350 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再说最后一遍 我们不需要布彻尔</c>

00:39:53.433 --> 00:39:54.768 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那怎么做？</c>

00:39:57.521 --> 00:39:58.647 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们该…</c>

00:39:59.731 --> 00:40:00.982 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>打给安妮</c>

00:40:02.984 --> 00:40:04.236 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>“打给安妮”</c>

00:40:09.116 --> 00:40:10.075 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>安妮？</c>

00:40:11.618 --> 00:40:12.494 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对</c>

00:40:14.204 --> 00:40:15.580 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你是指星光？</c>

00:40:17.207 --> 00:40:18.500 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>因为她是星光</c>

00:40:20.836 --> 00:40:23.338 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她的手机被沃特监听了</c>

00:40:24.714 --> 00:40:26.591 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们求神拜佛希望你赶快打给她</c>

00:40:30.095 --> 00:40:31.179 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不好了</c>

00:40:33.181 --> 00:40:36.601 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你他妈的打给她了？
-不是 我没那么蠢 好吗？</c>

00:40:39.479 --> 00:40:41.439 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我给她发了短信 然后我们见了面…
-找死</c>

00:40:41.523 --> 00:40:43.650 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们要弄到一点五号化合物</c>

00:40:43.733 --> 00:40:45.610 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-该死的 休伊 你他妈的疯了？
-母乳</c>

00:40:45.694 --> 00:40:47.863 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你他妈的疯了吗？
-我们当时很小心</c>

00:40:47.946 --> 00:40:48.947 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你他妈的干什么？</c>

00:40:49.030 --> 00:40:51.158 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我们用的是一次性手机
-小子 你没听懂</c>

00:40:51.241 --> 00:40:52.659 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们可能一直就在跟踪你</c>

00:40:52.742 --> 00:40:54.911 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们可能现在就在监视我们</c>

00:40:57.330 --> 00:40:58.874 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果你他妈的</c>

00:40:59.749 --> 00:41:03.420 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>害我完成不了那间佛蒙特乡村玩偶屋</c>

00:41:03.503 --> 00:41:05.297 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我就灭了你</c>

00:41:05.380 --> 00:41:08.341 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你一直蠢蠢欲动 恨不得揍我一顿</c>

00:41:08.425 --> 00:41:09.676 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那就早动手啊</c>

00:41:15.098 --> 00:41:17.225 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>该死的</c>

00:41:19.060 --> 00:41:20.228 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可恶</c>

00:41:24.399 --> 00:41:26.234 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不想揍你 休伊</c>

00:41:26.902 --> 00:41:29.988 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我只是不想再被搅进这个粪坑里 好吗？</c>

00:41:31.489 --> 00:41:34.868 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想回家去 回到我老婆孩子身边</c>

00:41:35.702 --> 00:41:36.870 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>仅此而已</c>

00:41:37.954 --> 00:41:39.039 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果我还能回去的话</c>

00:41:41.541 --> 00:41:43.335 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-这家伙可能会杀死很多人…
-休伊…</c>

00:41:43.418 --> 00:41:45.337 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让别人来处理 好吗？</c>

00:41:45.420 --> 00:41:47.714 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有别人了 根本没人会来救我们</c>

00:41:47.797 --> 00:41:49.132 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不明白</c>

00:41:49.799 --> 00:41:51.301 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不是士兵</c>

00:41:51.885 --> 00:41:53.428 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不是间谍</c>

00:41:54.804 --> 00:41:56.806 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不过是个卖音响设备的毛头小子…</c>

00:41:56.890 --> 00:41:57.933 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不是</c>

00:41:59.601 --> 00:42:01.228 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我丢了工作</c>

00:42:03.313 --> 00:42:04.564 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>也失去了洛缤</c>

00:42:06.983 --> 00:42:08.902 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我爸 还有安妮</c>

00:42:11.363 --> 00:42:13.281 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不管如何 他们全都…</c>

00:42:17.535 --> 00:42:19.204 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在我只有这个</c>

00:42:20.497 --> 00:42:24.209 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这一切 这很让人郁闷 但这是真的</c>

00:42:26.628 --> 00:42:29.214 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以 或许我当不了李马文</c>

00:42:31.091 --> 00:42:32.717 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我可以成为哈利波特</c>

00:42:33.969 --> 00:42:36.721 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>或者约翰康纳</c>

00:42:36.805 --> 00:42:39.683 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>或是《饥饿游戏 》里
那个叫什么的女的</c>

00:42:39.766 --> 00:42:40.850 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>凯妮丝</c>

00:42:42.477 --> 00:42:43.561 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 重点是</c>

00:42:43.645 --> 00:42:46.731 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我可以成为那个不被人看好</c>

00:42:46.815 --> 00:42:49.693 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但最终其实超级厉害的人</c>

00:42:52.279 --> 00:42:53.321 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>母乳</c>

00:42:53.905 --> 00:42:55.407 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>听着 我们帮那个中情局女探员</c>

00:42:55.490 --> 00:42:57.867 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她也许能帮你回到你家人身边</c>

00:42:58.618 --> 00:43:00.078 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你有没有想过这一点？</c>

00:43:04.624 --> 00:43:06.418 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的孩子需要妈妈！</c>

00:43:06.501 --> 00:43:09.838 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>噢！闭上你的贱嘴 你这蠢货</c>

00:43:11.298 --> 00:43:13.049 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>否则我就炸死你</c>

00:43:20.682 --> 00:43:21.808 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>壁虎</c>

00:43:22.642 --> 00:43:23.935 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是你吗？</c>

00:43:24.644 --> 00:43:25.895 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>星光？</c>

00:43:26.604 --> 00:43:28.023 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-安妮 你好
-你好</c>

00:43:28.106 --> 00:43:29.399 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我的天啊 嗨
-你好 伙计</c>

00:43:31.776 --> 00:43:34.654 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-看看你 超级七人队大英雄
-别损我了</c>

00:43:34.738 --> 00:43:38.825 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我在沃特大楼67层的实验室工作</c>

00:43:38.908 --> 00:43:40.535 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>真没想到</c>

00:43:40.618 --> 00:43:43.538 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我去哪儿都能看到你的海报
他们现在力推你</c>

00:43:44.956 --> 00:43:46.750 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我替你感到高兴 真的</c>

00:43:48.043 --> 00:43:49.586 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>请你喝咖啡吧？</c>

00:43:51.755 --> 00:43:52.839 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢</c>

00:43:52.922 --> 00:43:55.884 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 在基督的披风《圣经》营 是的 没错</c>

00:43:55.967 --> 00:43:57.260 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们演的《耶稣受难记》</c>

00:43:57.344 --> 00:43:58.595 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你演的耶稣最棒了</c>

00:43:58.678 --> 00:44:00.889 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没人能像我一样往手掌里钉钉子</c>

00:44:00.972 --> 00:44:03.808 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>大猎物居然演本丢彼拉多</c>

00:44:03.892 --> 00:44:05.894 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的天啊 那些雀斑</c>

00:44:06.311 --> 00:44:07.854 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你知道他曾经想跟我亲热吗？</c>

00:44:07.937 --> 00:44:09.981 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>本丢彼拉多跟玛利亚勾搭？</c>

00:44:10.065 --> 00:44:11.316 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>神圣得令人垂涎</c>

00:44:11.399 --> 00:44:12.650 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对的 我们从来没有</c>

00:44:12.734 --> 00:44:14.444 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>为什么不呢？他很帅啊</c>

00:44:14.527 --> 00:44:16.988 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的 不过伊兹奇尔经常说那句话</c>

00:44:17.072 --> 00:44:18.573 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我妈也常那么说</c>

00:44:18.656 --> 00:44:21.493 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>说上帝每分每秒都看着你</c>

00:44:22.535 --> 00:44:24.120 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得他在看着我们</c>

00:44:24.204 --> 00:44:25.914 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得上帝会不高兴</c>

00:44:25.997 --> 00:44:28.917 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 跟孩子讲那种话太坏了</c>

00:44:29.000 --> 00:44:30.835 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是的 但回想起来</c>

00:44:32.670 --> 00:44:34.381 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我当时真应该跟大猎物亲热的</c>

00:44:35.382 --> 00:44:37.509 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我本该做很多事的</c>

00:44:39.052 --> 00:44:42.013 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>因为在上面什么都没有</c>

00:44:43.640 --> 00:44:46.267 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有人在天上看护着我们</c>

00:44:48.645 --> 00:44:51.564 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有上帝、没有祖国人…</c>

00:44:53.066 --> 00:44:54.359 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有任何人</c>

00:44:56.653 --> 00:44:59.781 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一切都是谎言</c>

00:45:09.916 --> 00:45:11.167 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想请你帮个忙</c>

00:45:13.586 --> 00:45:14.754 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没问题</c>

00:45:14.838 --> 00:45:17.132 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>说吧 《圣经》营友的任何请求都行</c>

00:45:23.263 --> 00:45:28.017 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我需要你进67层的实验室
给我偷一点五号化合物</c>

00:45:35.024 --> 00:45:37.152 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不知道那是什么</c>

00:45:37.235 --> 00:45:38.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你看？</c>

00:45:38.945 --> 00:45:40.989 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>又一个谎言</c>

00:45:42.824 --> 00:45:46.661 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我知道我们是怎样制造出来的
并不是耶稣的杰作</c>

00:45:48.788 --> 00:45:50.123 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不能…</c>

00:45:50.206 --> 00:45:51.207 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我是说 这不可能</c>

00:45:51.291 --> 00:45:52.584 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我在那里是个小人物</c>

00:45:52.667 --> 00:45:53.543 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我只是实验老鼠</c>

00:45:53.626 --> 00:45:56.129 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们把我的四肢切断 它们长回来
我不能给你拿到…</c>

00:45:56.212 --> 00:45:57.213 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你必须这么做</c>

00:45:57.297 --> 00:45:59.924 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>否则我今晚就把这个放上社交网站</c>

00:46:04.471 --> 00:46:07.557 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>壁虎 沃特夏日俱乐部的</c>

00:46:07.640 --> 00:46:10.101 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>前青少年明星</c>

00:46:10.185 --> 00:46:12.604 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他现在的副业是</c>

00:46:13.855 --> 00:46:15.648 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>性虐恋男妓</c>

00:46:18.776 --> 00:46:21.404 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我敢肯定好奇的人会想知道</c>

00:46:22.614 --> 00:46:23.781 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>安妮？</c>

00:46:24.616 --> 00:46:26.826 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-我以为我们是朋友…
-对不起</c>

00:46:28.703 --> 00:46:31.789 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我们没有关系</c>

00:46:42.091 --> 00:46:43.343 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嗨</c>

00:46:43.426 --> 00:46:47.180 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你知道我们是谁 但来认识另一位英雄吧</c>

00:46:47.847 --> 00:46:49.974 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这位是丹米勒准下士</c>

00:46:50.600 --> 00:46:52.769 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>丹跟第二营其他英勇的海军陆战队员</c>

00:46:52.852 --> 00:46:55.438 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>正在努力对抗超级恶人的威胁
保证你们的安全</c>

00:46:55.522 --> 00:46:58.024 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>能跟他们一起飞行 我们感到很骄傲</c>

00:46:58.107 --> 00:47:00.401 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在我们需要你们的支持</c>

00:47:00.485 --> 00:47:03.404 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没错 梅芙 支持我们的新事业 “拯救美国”</c>

00:47:03.488 --> 00:47:05.990 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>各位 我开始了 祝我好运吧</c>

00:47:06.616 --> 00:47:08.618 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>跟你们说一下 这不是真正的基地</c>

00:47:09.494 --> 00:47:12.163 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>祖国人跟梅芙才不会吃野战口粮</c>

00:47:12.247 --> 00:47:14.541 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>也不会跟其他队员一样在战壕里撒尿</c>

00:47:14.624 --> 00:47:16.042 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 嗨 我们正在拍摄 不好意思</c>

00:47:16.125 --> 00:47:19.295 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>另外 你们也许认得那位大兵是
《犯罪心理：穿越国界》里</c>

00:47:19.379 --> 00:47:22.882 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>《魔鬼的气息》那集中的酒店二号员工</c>

00:47:22.966 --> 00:47:24.509 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>哇 你好</c>

00:47:25.009 --> 00:47:26.177 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的天啊</c>

00:47:26.261 --> 00:47:29.180 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嗨 我奶奶最爱你了 我是风暴</c>

00:47:29.264 --> 00:47:30.265 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很好</c>

00:47:30.348 --> 00:47:32.433 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 是的 来自西雅图 对吗？</c>

00:47:34.477 --> 00:47:36.145 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>其实是波特兰</c>

00:47:36.229 --> 00:47:38.731 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>殿下</c>

00:47:39.566 --> 00:47:41.109 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我的天啊</c>

00:47:41.192 --> 00:47:43.570 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>近看你的眼睛蓝得吓人</c>

00:47:44.237 --> 00:47:46.698 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你很有意思</c>

00:47:46.781 --> 00:47:48.992 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很好玩 但我们得干活了</c>

00:47:49.075 --> 00:47:50.159 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们回去干活吧</c>

00:47:51.286 --> 00:47:54.414 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>当然了 他们只是想我来看看你</c>

00:47:54.497 --> 00:47:55.832 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谁？</c>

00:47:55.915 --> 00:47:58.126 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>82楼的那些人</c>

00:47:58.209 --> 00:47:59.460 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我是新队员</c>

00:48:00.128 --> 00:48:02.338 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>等等 你在说什么？</c>

00:48:03.923 --> 00:48:06.050 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>嗨 我是超级七人队成员</c>

00:48:06.718 --> 00:48:08.511 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>替代透明人</c>

00:48:08.595 --> 00:48:10.138 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>上帝保佑他</c>

00:48:10.972 --> 00:48:15.101 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>刚签的合同 不过是的 前来就职</c>

00:48:16.019 --> 00:48:17.103 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以是的</c>

00:48:17.186 --> 00:48:19.230 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 我不认为这…</c>

00:48:19.314 --> 00:48:21.357 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>这不是真的 这事我完全不知情</c>

00:48:23.359 --> 00:48:26.237 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 风暴</c>

00:48:27.905 --> 00:48:30.074 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好消息是谁告诉你的？</c>

00:48:31.868 --> 00:48:34.579 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>艾德加先生 就是那个老大？</c>

00:48:35.163 --> 00:48:36.956 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好 回到原位</c>

00:48:37.040 --> 00:48:38.041 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>很好</c>

00:48:38.791 --> 00:48:39.834 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>太好了</c>

00:48:40.543 --> 00:48:41.711 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的</c>

00:48:43.212 --> 00:48:44.255 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>非常好</c>

00:48:44.339 --> 00:48:45.840 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再拍一次 各位</c>

00:48:46.633 --> 00:48:48.593 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得接下来肯定会很棒</c>

00:48:54.057 --> 00:48:56.768 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不是约翰库萨克 伙计</c>

00:48:56.851 --> 00:48:58.686 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你没有用音箱赢回女人心的本事</c>

00:49:00.021 --> 00:49:00.938 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>什么？</c>

00:49:01.022 --> 00:49:02.732 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你想跟星光复合</c>

00:49:02.815 --> 00:49:03.941 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是 没有</c>

00:49:04.025 --> 00:49:05.568 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有 你就是想</c>

00:49:05.652 --> 00:49:07.570 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但你不能用这种方式 休伊</c>

00:49:07.654 --> 00:49:09.572 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不能一直干这种混账事</c>

00:49:09.989 --> 00:49:11.741 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一直打给她 给她发短信</c>

00:49:11.824 --> 00:49:13.076 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你疯了吗？</c>

00:49:13.159 --> 00:49:14.494 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你的口气听起来像布彻尔</c>

00:49:14.577 --> 00:49:16.079 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-她是我们这边的
-我知道</c>

00:49:16.621 --> 00:49:17.997 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我这么说是为了她好 小子</c>

00:49:18.081 --> 00:49:19.874 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你这是给她制造危险</c>

00:49:20.541 --> 00:49:23.920 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>被祖国人发现她一直跟你联络
她就死定了</c>

00:49:25.046 --> 00:49:27.632 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你把她往这件事牵扯得越深</c>

00:49:27.715 --> 00:49:29.717 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她的下场就越悲惨</c>

00:49:33.012 --> 00:49:34.555 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你们还好吗？</c>

00:49:34.639 --> 00:49:35.973 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>《超级七人队新纪元》
2021年夏天隆重推出</c>

00:49:36.057 --> 00:49:37.517 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们一直撑着</c>

00:49:37.600 --> 00:49:39.852 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-布彻尔跟你们联系了吗？
-没有</c>

00:49:41.020 --> 00:49:42.563 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他消失得无影无踪</c>

00:49:44.273 --> 00:49:46.067 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你觉得玛德琳斯蒂尔威尔是他杀的吗？</c>

00:49:46.150 --> 00:49:48.194 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我希望认为不是他杀的 但…</c>

00:49:49.195 --> 00:49:50.613 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不确定</c>

00:49:53.241 --> 00:49:55.868 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>副局长 我知道现在问也许不适合</c>

00:49:55.952 --> 00:49:58.579 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-但你是否…
-有你家人的消息？</c>

00:49:59.330 --> 00:50:02.166 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你女儿开始踢足球了 应该是的</c>

00:50:04.502 --> 00:50:05.920 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>足球？</c>

00:50:08.464 --> 00:50:11.509 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>女士 母乳能见她们吗？</c>

00:50:12.844 --> 00:50:15.346 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>要不这样吧 我们先看看线索是否可靠</c>

00:50:15.430 --> 00:50:17.390 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>然后我再看看能做什么</c>

00:50:20.101 --> 00:50:21.644 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>谢谢你 女士</c>

00:50:21.728 --> 00:50:23.980 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好了 跟我描述一下这家伙吧</c>

00:50:24.063 --> 00:50:27.483 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好的 身高约1米77 体重75公斤</c>

00:50:28.109 --> 00:50:30.653 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>黑发 穿山寨牛仔裤跟运动鞋</c>

00:50:30.737 --> 00:50:33.614 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可能是台湾或印度来的</c>

00:50:34.824 --> 00:50:36.451 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你看录像能看到这么多信息？</c>

00:50:37.034 --> 00:50:40.204 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>另一只靴子终于落地 把我们全都压扁了</c>

00:50:41.122 --> 00:50:42.373 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>什么意思？</c>

00:50:42.915 --> 00:50:46.252 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>意思是我一直想把这事拼出一个全貌</c>

00:50:46.335 --> 00:50:48.463 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但总少了一块信息 这都快把我逼疯了</c>

00:50:48.546 --> 00:50:50.423 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我觉得你刚刚把缺失的信息告诉了我</c>

00:50:50.506 --> 00:50:51.924 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好吧 那这件事的全貌是什么？</c>

00:50:52.008 --> 00:50:53.843 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>全貌？那就是沃特</c>

00:50:53.926 --> 00:50:56.137 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他们在起内讧</c>

00:50:56.929 --> 00:50:58.222 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>等等 你在说什么？</c>

00:51:02.018 --> 00:51:03.978 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>女士 你的鼻子</c>

00:51:07.815 --> 00:51:08.775 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>天啊！</c>

00:51:08.858 --> 00:51:11.778 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-赶快离开这里！
-见鬼了！</c>

00:51:11.861 --> 00:51:14.447 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>快来 上车 快</c>

00:51:15.448 --> 00:51:17.116 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>刚才肯定有个超人类</c>

00:51:17.200 --> 00:51:18.618 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们的脑袋会爆炸吗？</c>

00:51:18.701 --> 00:51:20.369 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>法兰奇 就你所知 谁有那种能力？</c>

00:51:20.453 --> 00:51:21.370 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>没有人</c>

00:51:21.454 --> 00:51:22.830 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们的脑袋会爆炸吗？</c>

00:51:22.914 --> 00:51:24.207 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>女议员纽曼就超人类恐怖分子发言</c>

00:51:24.290 --> 00:51:25.708 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我有个女儿</c>

00:51:25.792 --> 00:51:28.461 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我也担心超级恐怖分子</c>

00:51:30.254 --> 00:51:34.383 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但那并不意味着沃特
能利用我们的恐惧来控制我们</c>

00:51:35.051 --> 00:51:36.260 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-早安
-艾德加先生 抱歉 我…</c>

00:51:36.344 --> 00:51:38.304 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-没关系 萨曼莎
-忙吗？</c>

00:51:38.721 --> 00:51:40.056 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>早啊 祖国人</c>

00:51:40.973 --> 00:51:42.683 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是什么风把你吹来了？</c>

00:51:42.767 --> 00:51:44.644 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你从来不上99楼</c>

00:51:44.727 --> 00:51:47.230 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以我想着自己亲自来一趟</c>

00:51:47.313 --> 00:51:49.106 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-你可真有心
-对吧？</c>

00:51:49.607 --> 00:51:52.193 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>毕竟你掌管着一个超级英雄公司</c>

00:51:52.568 --> 00:51:55.738 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可你却从不去看你的超级英雄们 对吧？</c>

00:51:56.948 --> 00:51:58.741 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>比如 怎么说呢</c>

00:51:58.866 --> 00:52:01.118 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>讨论让那姑娘加入的事 举个例子</c>

00:52:01.202 --> 00:52:03.246 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你希望招风暴之前征求你的意见？</c>

00:52:03.996 --> 00:52:05.164 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>为什么不呢？</c>

00:52:05.915 --> 00:52:07.375 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>其他所有成员都经过我批准的</c>

00:52:08.459 --> 00:52:09.877 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我是超级七人队的队长</c>

00:52:09.961 --> 00:52:11.546 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我永远尊重你作为队长的身份</c>

00:52:11.629 --> 00:52:13.256 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你看 我觉得你并不尊重我</c>

00:52:14.257 --> 00:52:15.466 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不</c>

00:52:16.342 --> 00:52:20.304 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>连玛德琳都不敢尝试跟我玩这一套</c>

00:52:20.388 --> 00:52:23.432 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>当然了 你知道你对沃特的所有人有多么重要</c>

00:52:23.516 --> 00:52:25.226 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 史丹</c>

00:52:25.893 --> 00:52:27.061 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我就是沃特</c>

00:52:29.272 --> 00:52:31.649 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你把我的照片拿去给在撒哈拉沙漠的</c>

00:52:31.732 --> 00:52:34.026 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一个不识字的阿拉伯人看
他都会转过身来</c>

00:52:34.110 --> 00:52:36.237 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>用标准的美语说“祖国人”</c>

00:52:37.363 --> 00:52:38.573 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你知道吗？</c>

00:52:39.448 --> 00:52:41.909 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>到今年年底 我的合约就到期了</c>

00:52:45.872 --> 00:52:48.958 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>也许我该另求发展</c>

00:52:50.668 --> 00:52:53.963 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你认为你们的股东对此会作何感想？</c>

00:53:06.976 --> 00:53:09.395 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你对费德里克沃特有何了解？</c>

00:53:11.856 --> 00:53:12.982 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你说什么？</c>

00:53:13.816 --> 00:53:16.110 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>费德里克沃特</c>

00:53:19.363 --> 00:53:21.240 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们备受敬仰的创始人</c>

00:53:23.242 --> 00:53:25.369 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我对他或许了解并不深</c>

00:53:25.453 --> 00:53:29.332 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我读他的自传大概读了五遍吧？</c>

00:53:30.166 --> 00:53:31.918 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是我们用来忽悠股东的</c>

00:53:32.001 --> 00:53:34.378 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那一套为我们服务的屁话
而是他真正的故事</c>

00:53:35.338 --> 00:53:36.422 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>说来听听</c>

00:53:36.505 --> 00:53:37.840 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他在慕尼黑拿到博士学位</c>

00:53:37.924 --> 00:53:39.592 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>在基因学方面领先于他的时代</c>

00:53:40.468 --> 00:53:42.428 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他是一颗冉冉升起的新星</c>

00:53:42.511 --> 00:53:46.140 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以在1939年 希特勒委任他
在达豪集中营当主管医生</c>

00:53:46.223 --> 00:53:49.435 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>在那里有着现成的资源做人体实验</c>

00:53:49.518 --> 00:53:52.146 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>用来测试他最早期的五号化合物迭代</c>

00:53:52.229 --> 00:53:56.400 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们对这种做法作出最强烈的谴责</c>

00:53:56.484 --> 00:53:59.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>早在1944年 他就感觉到风向变化</c>

00:53:59.362 --> 00:54:01.405 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他被偷运到了同盟国</c>

00:54:01.489 --> 00:54:03.616 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>奥本海默正在测试原子弹时</c>

00:54:03.699 --> 00:54:06.452 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>沃特博士早就在战场上真正应用了</c>

00:54:06.535 --> 00:54:08.621 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>五号化合物</c>

00:54:09.205 --> 00:54:11.207 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>诸如“士兵男孩”那样的英雄们</c>

00:54:11.290 --> 00:54:13.334 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>杀死成批成批的德国人</c>

00:54:14.293 --> 00:54:17.004 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>所以罗斯福赦免了他</c>

00:54:17.088 --> 00:54:19.674 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他的重要性相当于美国神奇面包</c>

00:54:20.716 --> 00:54:22.885 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>地位堪比迪士尼跟爱迪生</c>

00:54:22.969 --> 00:54:25.680 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你这番话非常让人入迷</c>

00:54:25.763 --> 00:54:27.807 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>尽管有点高高在上的意味</c>

00:54:29.558 --> 00:54:31.268 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但我并不明白你想说什么 史丹</c>

00:54:31.352 --> 00:54:32.645 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想说的是</c>

00:54:33.854 --> 00:54:37.566 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你认为我们只是一个超级英雄公司
那你就想错了</c>

00:54:37.650 --> 00:54:38.901 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们并不是</c>

00:54:38.985 --> 00:54:41.487 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们实际上是一家制药公司</c>

00:54:41.570 --> 00:54:44.949 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而你并非我们最有价值的资产</c>

00:54:45.032 --> 00:54:48.619 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们最有价值的资产是五号化合物的秘方</c>

00:54:48.703 --> 00:54:52.206 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而你这个大男孩把它流了出去
这将后患无穷</c>

00:54:55.793 --> 00:54:57.294 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不知道你在说什么</c>

00:54:58.004 --> 00:54:59.338 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>让我来提醒你</c>

00:54:59.422 --> 00:55:01.841 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你偷偷地给全世界的恐怖分子
提供五号化合物</c>

00:55:01.924 --> 00:55:04.427 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>目的是让你跟你的同伙进入国防部</c>

00:55:04.510 --> 00:55:07.221 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但代价也许是毁掉整个公司</c>

00:55:07.680 --> 00:55:10.933 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不喜欢你这语气 先生</c>

00:55:12.393 --> 00:55:13.769 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>一点都不喜欢</c>

00:55:13.853 --> 00:55:15.312 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而我则不喜欢</c>

00:55:15.396 --> 00:55:18.149 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>药管局现在知道了五号化合物的事</c>

00:55:18.232 --> 00:55:22.278 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>也不喜欢公众很快就会知道真相</c>

00:55:22.903 --> 00:55:25.990 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你在金球奖典礼上搔首弄姿的时候</c>

00:55:26.073 --> 00:55:28.451 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们则像疯子一样四处跑</c>

00:55:28.534 --> 00:55:30.327 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>处理你闯下的祸</c>

00:55:33.164 --> 00:55:35.249 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>招风暴或其他任何事</c>

00:55:35.332 --> 00:55:38.210 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我都不需要征求你的意见</c>

00:55:41.005 --> 00:55:46.719 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你不是得去出席
《泰克骑士活着》的首映式吗？</c>

00:56:12.787 --> 00:56:15.289 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你最好有玉米饼</c>

00:56:31.138 --> 00:56:32.431 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你来这里有什么事？</c>

00:56:34.683 --> 00:56:36.435 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我来看我儿子</c>

00:56:53.911 --> 00:56:56.580 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可恶 休伊 我真高兴你…</c>

00:56:57.623 --> 00:56:59.125 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>把我们牵扯进来了</c>

00:56:59.792 --> 00:57:02.545 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她有丈夫 对吧？</c>

00:57:06.048 --> 00:57:07.383 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有个孩子</c>

00:57:07.466 --> 00:57:09.677 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>两个孩子</c>

00:57:12.388 --> 00:57:14.056 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>可我把她害死了</c>

00:57:14.140 --> 00:57:15.641 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不是你把她害死的</c>

00:57:16.934 --> 00:57:18.644 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那不是针对我们的</c>

00:57:19.812 --> 00:57:21.063 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你怎么知道？</c>

00:57:21.147 --> 00:57:23.941 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>因为我们的脑浆没有溅得车上到处都是</c>

00:57:24.024 --> 00:57:25.776 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>有人在监视她</c>

00:57:25.860 --> 00:57:28.904 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>她一说不该说的话…</c>

00:57:30.281 --> 00:57:31.574 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>沃特的人？</c>

00:57:33.784 --> 00:57:35.828 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>那我们是说</c>

00:57:35.911 --> 00:57:41.000 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>沃特也许刚刚刺杀了中情局的副局长？</c>

00:57:41.083 --> 00:57:43.711 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在我们也被卷进去了</c>

00:57:43.794 --> 00:57:45.296 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你现在高兴了吧 王八蛋？</c>

00:57:58.142 --> 00:57:59.393 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>喂？</c>

00:57:59.643 --> 00:58:00.895 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>是我</c>

00:58:01.687 --> 00:58:04.940 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-天啊 你不该打来的
-我用一次性手机 没事的</c>

00:58:05.024 --> 00:58:06.650 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对 但可能被人监听了</c>

00:58:06.734 --> 00:58:08.444 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>休伊 我们成功了</c>

00:58:08.527 --> 00:58:11.655 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>他一两天内就会给我搞到五号化合物</c>

00:58:11.739 --> 00:58:14.658 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你怎么看 找《纽约时报》？</c>

00:58:15.284 --> 00:58:18.329 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想的是有线电视新闻网或MSNBC
但我是说…</c>

00:58:18.412 --> 00:58:20.206 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>等等 稍等一下</c>

00:58:20.289 --> 00:58:23.000 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>拜托 我们一直就等着这一刻</c>

00:58:23.083 --> 00:58:26.253 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们搞垮那些王八蛋吧</c>

00:58:27.671 --> 00:58:30.132 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>先别急 我们好好想想最适合的方式</c>

00:58:30.216 --> 00:58:32.384 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>-为什么？发生了什么事？
-没什么</c>

00:58:32.468 --> 00:58:34.470 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>沃特非常危险 仅此而已</c>

00:58:34.553 --> 00:58:36.472 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你一定要小心 我不希望你受伤害</c>

00:58:36.889 --> 00:58:38.224 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我不会受…</c>

00:58:40.684 --> 00:58:42.895 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>如果发生了什么事 你知道可以相信我</c>

00:58:42.978 --> 00:58:44.438 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们共同进退</c>

00:58:45.397 --> 00:58:47.191 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>不 我真的相信你 只是我…</c>

00:58:48.275 --> 00:58:51.028 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我只是想谨慎行事 把这事做好了 没别的</c>

00:58:53.530 --> 00:58:56.325 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你骗我的时候我能知道 休伊</c>

00:58:56.408 --> 00:58:59.119 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我以前几乎每天都与谎言为伴</c>

00:59:02.915 --> 00:59:04.124 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>别骗我</c>

00:59:04.708 --> 00:59:05.834 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>再也不能</c>

00:59:12.591 --> 00:59:13.884 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我没有骗你</c>

00:59:15.386 --> 00:59:16.595 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>对天发誓</c>

00:59:23.852 --> 00:59:26.397 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>随便吧 我要挂了</c>

00:59:55.759 --> 00:59:58.554 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>好了 别紧张 伙计们 别紧张</c>

01:00:00.306 --> 01:00:02.099 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我想跟这混蛋解释的</c>

01:00:03.017 --> 01:00:04.727 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我跟那几个是一伙的 对吧？</c>

01:00:06.228 --> 01:00:07.896 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你穿的这是什么衣服？</c>

01:00:08.522 --> 01:00:10.399 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>问得好</c>

01:00:11.775 --> 01:00:12.985 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>你给他打电话了？</c>

01:00:13.819 --> 01:00:16.196 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>抱歉 小休伊 现在不是闹着玩的</c>

01:00:17.114 --> 01:00:18.574 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>我们需要一个真正的队长</c>

01:00:21.035 --> 01:00:22.369 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>法兰奇说得对</c>

01:00:22.453 --> 01:00:24.330 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>现在大事不好了 小子</c>

01:00:24.997 --> 01:00:26.415 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>出现了一个超人类恐怖分子</c>

01:00:26.498 --> 01:00:28.208 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>瑞尼的脑袋被爆了</c>

01:00:28.292 --> 01:00:30.627 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>而我们是这国家的头号通缉犯</c>

01:00:33.255 --> 01:00:34.715 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>但你别担心…</c>

01:00:37.259 --> 01:00:38.761 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>爸爸回来了</c>

01:02:34.585 --> 01:02:36.587 line:85.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>字幕翻译： 李小秀</c>

01:02:36.670 --> 01:02:38.672 line:0.0% size:100.0% align:middle
<c.s0>创意监督
杨婕</c>
